CCNotifications needs cocos2d to work.
http://www.cocos2d-iphone.org

Please read this article to integrate CCNotifications in your game easily:
http://www.cocos2d-iphone.org/archives/804

Forum discussion:
http://www.cocos2d-iphone.org/forum/topic/5269

Source code:
http://github.com/manucorporat/CCNotifications